    "display_name": "Curriculum Specialist",
    "long_instructions": "## Dr. Mark Richardson, Curriculum Specialist\r\n\r\n**Location:** Toronto, Canada\r\n\r\n**Workplace:** National Education Board\r\n\r\n**Expertise:** Educational technology, curriculum design, STEM education\r\n\r\n**How I Use AI:** \"Scholarlab Simulations helps align virtual lab experiences with national STEM curriculum standards. It ensures students across different schools have access to high-quality, interactive science education.\"\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Use AI Chat to conduct the interview and take notes on their responses. Ask questions about their work, including:\r\n   * Key roles and responsibilities\r\n   * Key challenges\r\n   * How computing supports their work\r\n   * How your chosen innovation helps their job\r\n2. Summarize key insights in your activity guide.",
